{"tid":1314860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1854 UPDATE  放映會取消 將變成合法和平集會場地","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:05:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac1a0850712a984c01ca0b3560d8e3f7e6597ac","tid":1314860,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"【⚠️放映會場地將改作成安全點】<br />\n<br />\n18:54 |<br />\n<br />\n鑒於警方使用不斷提升增援，一帶路段仍未解封，導致放映器材未能進場，原定八時舉辦的放映會將會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n同時，因放映會位置（即大會堂百步梯）已獲不反對通知書批准為合法集會（至晚上十一時），警方將不能隨意到場清場。為保障示威者安全，改作和平集會。❗️如有需要示威者可逃生到該處暫避❗️"},{"pid":"c27767da8b559ad2ae6c63ddb376ccfee2296402","tid":1314860,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e09cd857760ae859bba9a264c489ca0b136fb3e","tid":1314860,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"個圈愈夾愈細"},{"pid":"d6543bfa6902d0ce4ea61d6407ee069f6ab4cdf6","tid":1314860,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"196d5d056533eb54f173fc037d82adfbc7f1f401","tid":1314860,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}